summary: Rumor: Nintendo will bring out two new Switch models this year
title: Rumor: Nintendo will bring out two new Switch models this year
body:
Rumor: Nintendo will bring out two new Switch models this year

The Wall Street Journal reports that Nintendo is actively working on two new models for the active hybrid console Switch. According to WSJ, these two models will certainly be different in terms of design and may come early this summer.

Takashi Mochizuki cut the news behind the pay wall, but what’s most important is that Nintendo wants to double the surprise big success by offering two new…
